Summary: Objects appear in photos taken in the dark with digital camera
divs: Sighting DetailsFrom May to September 2008 we have been photographing these objects in the dark with a digital camera. We have possibly 100 pictures of them. We have photographed them in the house also. You can not see them with your naked eye. They seem to resemble the photo at the top of page 4 of the September, 2008 MUFON Journal.
